{"tid":591904,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"帶水槍回前公司「報仇」　男反遭前主管暴打","createTime":"2018-03-14T00:31:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-14T01:30:53.000Z","uid":72478,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"748a4610d159e73e19b5b75e7ea820e23bd0dd4b","tid":591904,"uid":72478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T00:31:39.000Z","msg":"片: <a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20180314/1314265/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20180314%2F1314265%2F&d=W%2BH%2FhQi2htBT%2FNrt%2BuYF%2FF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=04d049d6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20180314%2F1314265%2F&h=f3bf2c86\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20180314/1314265/</a><br />\n<br />\n中國四川宜賓翠屏區一名張姓男子，因為不堪洪姓主管刁難，日前辭去汽車銷售店的工作。但他後來越想越氣，於是周一（12日）帶水槍回到公司，水射對方報復。不料，此舉引起洪男暴怒，把他追打到身體多處受傷。張男事後要求洪男道歉，聲稱會提起民事訴訟。<br />\n<br />\n汽車店員工透露，張男本月初才離職，而理由是受到洪男排擠，感到心裡很不舒服。張男承認，噴水槍確實有不恰當之處，但認為自己反被打到身體受傷，是洪男防衞過當造成的，若對方沒有明確致歉，就要提起民事訴訟。（大陸中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180314/640_f620e318ea343d62fcf2e2d71b7cd6ec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180314%2F640_f620e318ea343d62fcf2e2d71b7cd6ec.jpg&h=6acc855c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180314/640_af83f65cfbe9db52c2fa51119c3702f4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180314%2F640_af83f65cfbe9db52c2fa51119c3702f4.jpg&h=4e9ad434&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2612c643bccd7f75a8f2fbb1436d8b6acd68ff5f","tid":591904,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T00:38:02.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4362f9d3861d1204d612b49a56fdb911cd7447d8","tid":591904,"uid":122798,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T00:39:21.000Z","msg":"諗起子華同劉青雲果段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"049cab7ba1a1812f26f6f5e14327b062fef4e6bb","tid":591904,"uid":144843,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T01:06:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ff4e28e26bca4b25bbc8b89e601d66514906d48a","tid":591904,"uid":33206,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T01:08:32.000Z","msg":"[quote]<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180314/640_f620e318ea343d62fcf2e2d71b7cd6ec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180314%2F640_f620e318ea343d62fcf2e2d71b7cd6ec.jpg&h=6acc855c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nquote]<br />\n呢張相好有喜感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f08bec0eb8f2fe2c618c16ea7bc631a725692102","tid":591904,"uid":4180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T01:17:57.000Z","msg":"喳架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd309e171a138efdd853d82c278e24befc7a0a93","tid":591904,"uid":162539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"049cab7ba1a1812f26f6f5e14327b062fef4e6bb","tid":591904,"uid":144843,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T01:06:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T01:19:21.000Z","msg":"裝尿好過用真槍啦，真係殺人咩"},{"pid":"4b4d6e6b813576ef649caee3938404397c8dd7ef","tid":591904,"uid":57513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4362f9d3861d1204d612b49a56fdb911cd7447d8","tid":591904,"uid":122798,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T00:39:21.000Z","msg":"諗起子華同劉青雲果段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T01:30:53.000Z",